@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nuzsdp(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = tmp
    tmp = wp.sin((wp.cos(tmp + 0.65) - (v1 + 0.57 * v1 + 0.30)))
    tmp = v1
    tmp = wp.cos(tmp)
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v0 + 0.40 - v0 + 0.24)))
    data[tid] = v0
